{"tid":1029703,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人係咪而家連少少禮貌都唔識","createTime":"2019-02-20T12:05:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-20T15:38:39.000Z","uid":1925,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"9b674a5c619a891b6e5e24f2851d6de88282c150","tid":1029703,"uid":1925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T12:05:32.000Z","msg":"話說岩岩返到樓下<br />\n後面有個廢中坑 拎住一袋二袋<br />\n咁通常人地無出聲叫等埋 我都會㩒實部𨋢等埋人入<br />\n吖佢個撚樣慢慢咁行都算 <br />\n唔該都無聲不特止 個閪口閪面<br />\n即刻想推佢個冚家剷埋牆 同佢講：講唔該呀屌你老母<br />\n以後唔撚幫人做揸𨋢人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d181da8bfcf3bb04a18e63fd633ac0e4d2a5ee3","tid":1029703,"uid":186844,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T12:14:27.000Z","msg":"又唔敢當面屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c68e4316eec03abb3dcb3d48cb446fc5fe6e0f3","tid":1029703,"uid":53122,"like":12,"dislike":3,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T12:22:45.000Z","msg":"施恩莫望報<br />\n<br />\n你做好人係你on9 啫<br />\n記得以後唔好做啦"},{"pid":"f0781f8231521c68b831a9b06a34c4416600f2de","tid":1029703,"uid":77474,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T13:08:13.000Z","msg":"咁咪等佢差唔多行到就閂門"},{"pid":"3d107d7c124d5e0e4cc20a938d0c02e772fc2c1e","tid":1029703,"uid":143970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4d181da8bfcf3bb04a18e63fd633ac0e4d2a5ee3","tid":1029703,"uid":186844,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T12:14:27.000Z","msg":"又唔敢當面屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T13:21:15.000Z","msg":"唔講唔該就無得屌既 <br />\n<br />\n人地無禮貌由佢  當佢垃圾咪得"},{"pid":"f784e254ae3c163cfa3420389f6d4d94db2f7b06","tid":1029703,"uid":215784,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T14:59:30.000Z","msg":"我代個廢老同你講聲唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港需要更多樓主呢類人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"